<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Westgate</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A tranquil residential neighborhood located in the South West quadrant of Calgary, Westgate was established in the year 1957 and is currently represented by the Ward 8 councilor in the Calgary City Council.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The neighborhood is surrounded by the Bow Trail and the Edworthy Park to the north, the Sarcee Trail on the west, 17 Avenue S on the south and the 45 Street W on the east side.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">With a variety of recreational venues including shopping complexes, hockey rinks, parks and sports fields located within the Westgate real estate, the residents have plenty options for entertainment.</p>
        </div>
